<h1>Your Turf Monster email was changed</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

<p>The email address on your Turf Monster account was just changed from <strong><%= @old_email %></strong> to <strong><%= @new_email %></strong>.</p>

<p><strong>Did you do this?</strong></p>

<p>If yes — nothing to do; we sent a verification link to your new email separately.</p>

<p>If no — your account may be compromised. Reply to this message or contact support immediately. Changing your password now will also boot anyone else who is signed in.</p>

<p>— Turf Monster</p>
